summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $302.50, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the general fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the 1910 general taxes on lost 1, 2, 3, 10, 11 and a part of lots 4, 5, 6, 7, 8 and 9, block 2, and part of lots 5 and 6, block 6, and lots 6 and 7, block 8, Burke's 1st Addition, and a part of lots 11 and 12, block 3, Supplemental Plat of block 3, Burke's 1st Addition, and lots 6 and 7, block 45, Lake Union Shore Lands.
